note inverted-pyramid.vrb — inverted centered star pyramid.
note Row i (counting down from rows) has (i-1) leading spaces and (2*i - 1) stars.

ask the user "how many rows?" and save to rows.

row = rows.
while row >= 1:
    sp = 1.
    spaces = rows - row.
    while sp <= spaces:
        display " ".
        sp += 1.
    end.
    stars = row * 2 - 1.
    col = 1.
    while col <= stars:
        display "*".
        col += 1.
    end.
    say.
    row -= 1.
end.
